title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 21, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 21, 2020
description:
ON today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, Dan recaps the wild week that was Week 2 in the NFL. Can the rash of injuries be attributed to a lack of preseason games? We're joined by NBA HoFer Reggie Miller and 2x Super Bowl Champion, Eli Manning. Plus, DP has some more information on Big Ten football and when we can expect to see Pac 12 football return.
